The Fremennik sea boots 2 is a reward from completing the medium Fremennik Diary tasks given to you by Thorodin south of Rellekka and can be retrieved from him for free if lost. Its stats are identical to those of Steel boots.

 Attack bonuses
+0+0+0-3-1

Benefits[edit | edit source]

From Fremennik sea boots 1[edit | edit source]

  • Peer the Seer will act as a bank deposit box
  • Fossegrimen will give your enchanted lyre an extra charge when making a sacrifice
  • One free teleport to Rellekka every day

Fremennik sea boots 2 only[edit | edit source]

  • Shortcut jump from Miscellania dock to Etceteria
  • Improved rate of gaining approval on Miscellania

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes

(update)

The item was graphically updated again.

(update)

1 March 2018
(update)

The item was graphically updated.

24 March 2016
(update | poll)
  • It is now also possible to get multiple copies of achievement diary equipment by talking to relevant diary masters or by talking to Perdu, found upstairs in the Edgeville general store. Perdu will charge a small fee.
  • The "Destroy" option was replaced with a "Drop" option.
